m.s3.amazonaws.com/politifact%2Fmugs%2Ftrump_1.jpg\">\r\n    <div class=\"speaker\">\r\n      <div class=\"speaker-name\">Donald Trump</div>\r\n      <div class=\"speaker-title\">Presidential candidate</div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"rating\">\r\n    <img src=\"http://fact-reporter.herokuapp.com/rating-images/politifact/tom-false.jpg\" />\r\n    <img src=\"http://static.politifact.com/mediapage/jpgs/politifact-logo-big.jpg\" />\r\n  </div>\r\n  <br />\r\n  <p>\r\n    The wives of the 9/11 hijackers \"knew exactly what was happening\" and went back to Saudi Arabia two days before the attacks to watch their husbands on television flying the planes.\r\n  </p>\r\n  <div class=\"dateline\">\r\n    \r\n      A presidential debate in Detroit \u2013 Thursday, March 3, 2016\r\n    \r\n  </div>\r\n  <ul class=\"menu\">\r\n    <li><a href=\"#factbox\" onclick='toggleShareVisibility(this)'>Share</a></li>\r\n    <li><a href=\"http://www.politifact.com/truth-o-meter/statements/2016/mar/03/donald-trump/donald-trump-repeats-false-claim-about-911-hijacke/\">Read more</a></li>\r\n      <div class=\"share\">\r\n          <a href=\"javascript:facebookShare('http://fact-reporter.herokuapp.com/share/d3deecb3-f7c5-4915-82c7-aab4897bb54d', 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/share-the-facts/d3deecb3-f7c5-4915-82c7-aab4897bb54d', 520, 350)\"><div class=\"share-button facebook\"><div class=\"share-label\"><i class=\"fa fa-facebook\"></i></div></div></a>\r\n\r\n          <a href=\"javascript:twitterShare('705800223491301377', 520, 350)\"><div class=\"share-button twitter\"><div class=\"share-label\"><i class=\"fa fa-twitter\"></i></div></div></a>\r\n      \r\n      <div class=\"embed-button\"><div class=\"embed-label\"><a href=\"#factbox\" onclick=\"toggleEmbedBox(this)\">Embed</a></div></div>\r\n          <textarea rows=\"4\" cols=\"50\" class=\"embed_box\"></textarea>\r\n\r\n      </div>\r\n  </ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\t\t\t\r\n", "ruling_comments_date": "2016-03-03T23:01:46.006442", "ruli